<GUID>[,<parameterPair>]*

Provider1 = {D857C50C-9002-4852-94A4-7264063CF38D} Provider2 = {9FD91669-452C-4B25-AD5B-5322D511DA65},level:Informational,KeywordsAny:0x1f0 Provider3 = {B7F33BAA-E45A-4FCF-8389-FA103A2AC23C},KeywordsAll:0x5
